{"tid":862354,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴黎聖日門正密切關注迪基亞，隨時準備出手","createTime":"2018-10-14T18:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T10:59:54.000Z","uid":124292,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d704ac03a70a78c1e6405d6adc34314a60d12012","tid":862354,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:33:18.000Z","msg":"曼聯門將迪基亞目前並不急於和球隊續約。<br />\n<br />\n此外，巴黎聖日門正在密切關注迪基亞的狀況。如果有機會的話，他們已經準備好出手了。<br />\n<br />\n目前，曼聯有11名球員的合約會在明年夏天到期，而迪基亞正是其中一位。<br />\n<br />\n《郵報》還談到了迪基亞的西班牙同胞，馬達和靴里拉的情況。《郵報》稱馬達正在等著曼聯給他新合約，亦有其他西班牙的球會對他有意。而靴里拉已經有一份新合約在手，不過待遇比他預計的要低。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-6274745/David-Gea-no-rush-sign-new-deal-Manchester-United-PSG-ready-swoop.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Farticle-6274745%2FDavid-Gea-no-rush-sign-new-deal-Manchester-United-PSG-ready-swoop.html&d=jebdwlTiQyTJVUSyhQpfif%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=ac248c20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-6274745/David-Gea-no-rush-sign-new-deal-Manchester-United-PSG-ready-swoop.html</a>"},{"pid":"a07c8673da2c140701104cf5755bdfa8cfb9da53","tid":862354,"uid":35598,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T20:41:09.000Z","msg":"P$G使唔使咁多個龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b98a191181b0669d634220ff06be75cd1681beb","tid":862354,"uid":216694,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:52:51.000Z","msg":"阿雷奧拉：？？？"},{"pid":"e70d3df3e505bcf9ebf429afa8a1eb673a277796","tid":862354,"uid":214972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:56:48.000Z","msg":"佢點過fairplay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"24dfc0cb4c1aa5b68be03e7699ec46103ffa9d0e","tid":862354,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a07c8673da2c140701104cf5755bdfa8c